    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed the required level. The single shortfall (Test conditions, achieved level 2 vs. required level 3) is offset by the direct correspondence between the ASTM F1717 validation scenario and the COU, the use of production-equivalent hardware, and cross-laboratory reproducibility across N=11 constructs. The overall credibility evidence is sufficient to support the Medium assurance level for this Class II device submission.",
